OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be dry with lengthy
OL,6,Fbright or sunny spells and feeling a
OL,7,Fbit warmer again. Sunshine turning
OL,8,Fhazy later as high cloud spreads
OL,9,Fsoutheast later in the afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FDry at first with some hazy
OL,12,Fevening sunshine. It will stay dry
OL,13,Fovernight, turning cloudy over
OL,14,Fnorthern Angus with some clear spells
OL,15,Fover Tayside and Fife.
OL,16,
OL,17,CMonday:FIt will be dry throughout the
OL,18,Fday with variable cloud and some warm
OL,19,Fsunny spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
